# Assignment 1 - Exploring NNs with pytorch

## Classification Analysis

Binary classification using binary cross-entropy loss function on k-mean blobs.

Multi-class classification, added blob centres and investigation of the effect of number of centres, data noise, dimension of the input.

## Regression

Prediction of numerical values using a regressor, using MSE (in essence MAE) loss function to evaluate the network and analysing the effect of changing network structure.

## Investigate Study

Hyperparameter tuning of the network to analyse the effects of extended training, batch size, and learning rate scheduling.
